
AI服务环境变量配置
请复制此文件为 .env.local 并填入您的真实API密钥

OpenAI配置
OPENAI_API_KEY=your-openai-api-key-here
OPENAI_API_BASE=https://api.openai.com/v1
OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o

文心大模型配置
ERNIE_API_KEY=your-ernie-api-key-here
ERNIE_SECRET_KEY=your-ernie-secret-key-here
ERNIE_API_BASE=https://aip.baidubce.com/rpc/2.0/ai_custom/v1/wenxinworkshop

语音识别服务配置
SPEECH_RECOGNITION_API_KEY=your-speech-api-key-here
SPEECH_RECOGNITION_API_BASE=https://speech.googleapis.com/v1

音视频处理服务配置
MEDIA_PROCESSING_API_KEY=your-media-api-key-here
MEDIA_PROCESSING_API_BASE=https://api.example.com/media

其他配置
AI_SERVICE_TIMEOUT=30000
AI_SERVICE_MAX_RETRIES=3
